<!--pages/persdata/persdata.wxml-->
<view>
  <view class="index-top">
      <view class="index-top-one" style="height:{{statusBarHeight}}px;position:fixed;top:0;left:0;z-index:111"></view>
      <view class="fixtop" style="position:fixed;top:{{statusBarHeight}}px;left:0;z-index:111">
        <view class="index-top-title">
          <van-icon style="margin-left:40rpx;" name="arrow-left" bindtap="backUp" />
          <text style="margin-left:-60rpx;"></text>
          <text> </text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="topBg">
      <image src="../../icon/bg1.png" mode="aspectFill" style="filter: blur(2px);"></image>
      <view class="avatar">
        <image src="../../icon/avatar1.png"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="persTitle">
        <image style="width:36rpx;height:33rpx;" src="../../icon/vip.png"></image>
        <text style="font-size:30rpx; color:#fff;margin-left:15rpx;">刘亦菲女神</text>
        <text class="sign">VIP会员</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="persDetail">
      <view class="persmodel">
        <text style="font-size: 30rpx;font-weight: 700;">个人资料</text>
        <view class="tagList">
          <text class="tag">女</text>
          <text class="tag">27岁</text>
          <text class="tag">173cm</text>
          <text class="tag">48kg</text>
          <text class="tag">未婚</text>
          <text class="tag">合肥庐阳区</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="persmodel">
        <text style="font-size: 30rpx;font-weight: 700;">择偶要求</text>
        <view class="tagList">
          <text class="tag">20-35岁</text>
          <text class="tag">171-185cm</text>
          <text class="tag">5-8千</text>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="persmodel">
        <text style="font-size: 30rpx;font-weight: 700;">个人独白</text>
        <view style="margin-top:0rpx">
          <text>
          我容易相处，为人实在，低调做人，踏实做事，懂得照顾呵护自己的女人是我最...
        </text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
</view>
